name hyphen-afrikaans
category TLCore
revision 78069
shortdesc Afrikaans hyphenation patterns.
longdesc Hyphenation patterns for Afrikaans in T1/EC and UTF-8
longdesc encodings. OpenOffice includes older patterns created by a
longdesc different author, but the patterns packaged with TeX are
longdesc considered superior in quality.
