catalogue-topics format

name latex-base-dev
category Package
revision 77483
shortdesc Development pre-release of the LaTeX kernel
longdesc This package provides a test release for upcoming LaTeX2e
longdesc kernel changes. Testing by the LaTeX team itself suggests that
longdesc the code is stable and usable, but wider use by knowledgeable
longdesc users is desired. The code here is used by TeX systems to
longdesc create dedicated formats, for example pdflatex-dev and
longdesc lualatex-dev, which can then be used explicitly for testing,
longdesc simply by changing your program invocation.
