name pst-barcode
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Print barcodes using PostScript
longdesc The pst-barcode package allows printing of barcodes, in a huge
longdesc variety of formats, including quick-response (qr) codes (see
longdesc documentation for details). As a PSTricks package, the package
longdesc requires pstricks. The package uses PostScript for calculating
longdesc the bars. For PDF output use a multi-pass mechanism such as
longdesc pst-pdf.
containersize 143220
