name wrapfig
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Produces figures which text can flow around
longdesc Allows figures or tables to have text wrapped around them. Does
longdesc not work in combination with list environments, but can be used
longdesc in a parbox or minipage, and in twocolumn format. Supports the
longdesc float package.
containersize 9352
containerchecksum ffa00259e8829c70cd76278c74c52807f174324e291ccdaa9e895b65d6fbeb77533bf85d5c0925ee224ffb6d0248e20f286fba9a3e8bbafdf24e7b93be332f2a
doccontainersize 337900
doccontainerchecksum 79deaffd84c468ead0cf7f942dca579d1547c8dc00a7b31f2286ebeea92ffffa1136c344ff6779cd2549c1c31e53bc3c4509d376dd5d8b159e5df1abccf378c2
docfiles size=87
 texmf-dist/doc/latex/wrapfig/multiple-span.txt details="How to use wrapfig to span multiple columns"
 texmf-dist/doc/latex/wrapfig/wrapfig-doc.pdf details="Package documentation"
 texmf-dist/doc/latex/wrapfig/wrapfig-doc.tex
runfiles size=7
 texmf-dist/tex/latex/wrapfig/wrapfig.sty
catalogue-also wrapfig2
catalogue-ctan /macros/latex/contrib/wrapfig
catalogue-license lppl
catalogue-topics text-flow tagged-pdf-incompatible
catalogue-version 3.6

name xcjk2uni
category Package
revision 54958
shortdesc Convert CJK characters to Unicode, in pdfTeX
longdesc The package provides commands to convert CJK characters to
longdesc Unicode in non-UTF-8 encoding; it provides hooks to support
longdesc hyperref in producing correct bookmarks. The bundle also
longdesc provides /ToUnicode mapping file(s) for a CJK subfont; these
longdesc can be used with the cmap package, allowing searches of, and
longdesc cut-and-paste operations on a PDF file generated by pdfTeX.
containersize 200052
